{
  "stem": "19921.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 304.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And one night, myself and my brother came back from work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] By the way, that brother now is my uncle, so that will come out later.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] In any event, we came back from work, and everybody was asleep in that house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the house was full of gas.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was no gas in that house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But the house was-- was built-- believe it or not, the house was built from bricks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But the brick was made from cow manure.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the condition where it was wintertime, and you close all the-- you know, in winter, you close the windows, OK?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in those particular houses, you're not supposed to have closed the windows.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're supposed to have left the windows open, because the heat exposed and somehow-- somehow developed gas from that thing, from the outside.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were half dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The whole family was half dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We ran to neighbors, and the neighbors called the-- the ambulance, whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The ambulances came in, and they dragged them out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "First of all, everybody-- we walk out, and out of the house to get some fresh air.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's the only thing which saved them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then they brought them to the ambulances, and they took them to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They survived, but we almost died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So-- [SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, there was another reason which we-- choose that-- I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I forgot that the main reason, actually, which we choose that-- that Engel's there, and Kolpashev, and Saratov.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because at that time, we heard that the Polish army is being organized in that area.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was our aim-- to get with the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we-- at that time, we knew that the Polish army takes the families.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
